{"tid":2099520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【仲有三日】初選資訊你睇咗未？","createTime":"2020-07-08T09:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T01:39:05.000Z","uid":20558,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"6648a54e92acde43fe0b5ae00b15ffb6d62366c2","tid":2099520,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 幾時喺邊度投？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>7.11-12</strong> 全港251個票站總有一個喺左近<br />\n<strong>9am-9pm</strong> 記得投票！<br />\n<br />\n港島<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ng60qz5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fng60qz5.png&h=7eb09865&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n九東<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwSu3mS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwSu3mS.png&h=1810148a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九西<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hGf4Sfh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhGf4Sfh.png&h=76d13537&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n新東<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLyuiVp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLyuiVp.png&h=d4db1c10&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n新西<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qKhsOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qKhsOQ.png&h=b6c91d3e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n衛生服務界<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bFFgJnj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbFFgJnj.png&h=a25b59b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"203507c279cfb3ac1b8a6829954671acbc37363d","tid":2099520,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 注意事項：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要帶 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>(任何一樣)</strong></span><br />\n1. 住址證明<br />\n2. 官方選舉選民通知書<br />\n3. 選民登記網站截圖（呢度cap）<span style=\"color: red;\">(最好cap定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2Findex.jsp&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=239e1eb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/index.jsp</a><br />\n證明你係嗰區居民/選民<br />\n<br />\n用自己電話去票站scan qr code 喺app投票<br />\n票站有少量後備公家機<br />\n部分票站有實體票（記得check咗邊個票站有先）<br />\n<br />\n要填<br />\n1. 身分證後四位數字（唔包括號內數字）<br />\n2. 身分證簽發日期（年月日）<br />\n3. 出生日期（日期ONLY）"},{"pid":"f0113bab711c587705c77f51dde5281ddfa91a18","tid":2099520,"uid":20558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:40:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 點樣投？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1️⃣ 服務站外用電話Scan QR Code<br />\n2️⃣ 下載<ins>普及投票 4.0 APP</ins> (Android機) 或進入投票網站 (IOS 機)<br />\n3️⃣ 進入投票程序<br />\n4️⃣ 輸入票站編號<br />\n5️⃣ 輸入個人資料及投票<br />\n6️⃣ 完成後會產生選票嘅 QR code<br />\n7️⃣ 行入票站搵工作人員 Scan 你電話上面嘅 QR code<br />\n8️⃣ 工作人員會核對你嘅身份<br />\n9️⃣ 確認及遞交電子選票<br />\n🔟 搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cH2yLPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcH2yLPa.png&h=a8f99662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGdicDw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGdicDw.png&h=2d629ad1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a16989ac21b3eaf026bd4a4a5d0b6e27e5ff065a","tid":2099520,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 訓咗冇睇，有咩候選人？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xwiRGVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxwiRGVK.jpg&h=d7ffab95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b8eeb9b6347115dc02850551d3a48c48e8ceb71","tid":2099520,"uid":20558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 睇完仲有好多問題望呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 睇完發現冇自己選區<br />\n投票跟番立法會分區就得 新東/新西/九東/九西/港島<br />\n區議會分區唔使理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子：屯門人去新西任何一個票站投都得，唔一定喺屯門投<br />\n<br />\n2. 地址證明<br />\ncap選民登記網都得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2Findex.jsp&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=239e1eb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/index.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 咩app投<br />\n去到票站scan qr code下載個app就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【An機可以down定先<br />\n初選投票 app 《普及投票 4.0》 (Andriod版)<br />\nGoogle Play: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.popvote.voter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.popvote.voter&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=56e05a9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.popvote.voter</a> 】<br />\n<br />\n4. 票站開放時間<br />\n大部分9am-9pm 但有個別票站會有唔同<br />\n<br />\n5. 投幾多票<br />\n地區一票+超區一票<br />\n前提當然係非功能組別選民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 有Google map喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1tiK9tjlTWPHXyHr0U28ReQ7b3OYr2H40&amp;ll=22.290909684527648%2C114.10864606425775&amp;z=10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1tiK9tjlTWPHXyHr0U28ReQ7b3OYr2H40%26ll%3D22.290909684527648%252C114.10864606425775%26z%3D10&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=dd45b46b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1tiK9tjlTWPHXyHr0U28ReQ7b3OYr2H40&amp;ll=22.290909684527648%2C114.10864606425775&amp;z=10</a>"},{"pid":"5e796b8d429b6822d3a47333c7625a2a6defb64f","tid":2099520,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 溫馨提示</span></span><br />\n1. 提早cap定選民登記冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知啦 個網係政府嘢嚟架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 搵多一兩個附近票站做後備<br />\n以防萬一 太多人 或者有咩突發事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 小心on9限聚令<br />\n票站太多人 就行開少少等啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 其實...我地係去搵區議員教我地用電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 記得拉埋啲姨媽姑姐三姑六婆去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77eb1e493a52a6fead51f2ceac7bf632eeb63d0","tid":2099520,"uid":20558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:42:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7. 有能力嘅支持下個眾籌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/democrats35plus/?fbclid=IwAR1fKPXFxQwohrgoaiUj6Uc3iTT-bwJFs5ys0nrNXJrV50sBRrCdcpgXHtk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fdemocrats35plus%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1fKPXFxQwohrgoaiUj6Uc3iTT-bwJFs5ys0nrNXJrV50sBRrCdcpgXHtk&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=36988c27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/democrats35plus/?fbclid=IwAR1fKPXFxQwohrgoaiUj6Uc3iTT-bwJFs5ys0nrNXJrV50sBRrCdcpgXHtk</a><br />\n<br />\n注意：選舉經費所限，每人捐款上限1000元"},{"pid":"5e6efcec7270f4c4d0804a1a5932735776ac07f5","tid":2099520,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2f08950baf85bbb5b3e8a1bfcde5cae357b117","tid":2099520,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c95a2e5da73fa7249f49549eac72739be824ff","tid":2099520,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:47:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e349c29c8dd099eda29b494ffe3751640a943d61","tid":2099520,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad10fedf432eb1bd3bfd153336175be4307b0863","tid":2099520,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:48:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e71120379ac881bec061a9be3bd4dd5193f0d00","tid":2099520,"uid":24102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:48:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38f93fc28c4416b0fb6ae5eed7d1d5d1c81bc55b","tid":2099520,"uid":24102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f549605d04c664179148d90d13f0af1d9e916e15","tid":2099520,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:48